PrecisSetting apart, for the use and benefit of the WUSKWI SIPIHK FIRST NATION, of some 747 hectares of land (known as the North Steeprock Lake selection) situated near the Village of Birch River, Manitoba, to be known as Wuskwi Sipihk First Nation Indian Reserve No. 8.
